creator: Mateusz Struk
descriptionHtml:
A new shiny, modern, third-party extended successor of Interpals application equipped with Material UI and much greater stability and performance.

Its still in development, right now at release candidate stage, so very soon final release is coming. What can I say to encourage you?
-no more crashed voice messages
-no more crashed photo uploads
-more gifs
-light & dark modes
-large amount of color themes for light modes
-works much, much faster than original app
-zero ads
-improved, animated UI in Material Design 3
-clickable links in messages/posts (YT links opens in YT app, not browser)

Check it out, any bug report or review is much appreciated! For now it supports Android 7.0 up to Android 13

Check out official Telegram group of OuterPals if you have any questions/bug reports/feature requests!
